# Flipper

Part of **yego-project** workspace. Full context: `../../AGENTS.md` at workspace root.

- Melos monorepo; `secrets.dart` not in git
- Brick + Ditto sync: `docs/ditto_sync.md`
- **Main Brick DB (native):** Turso via `PlatformHelpers.getMainDatabaseFactory()` — local `tursoDatabaseFactory()` or `tursoSyncDatabaseFactory()` when `tursoDatabaseUrl` + token are set in `secrets.dart`. Do not open `flipper.sqlite` with sqlite3 while the app runs.
- **Turso + get policies:** `open-sources/brick/docs/sqlite/turso_get_policies.md` — `awaitRemoteWhenNoneExist` / `alwaysHydrate` pull Turso Cloud before Supabase hydrate.
- **Offline HTTP queue:** sqflite only (`getQueueDatabaseFactory()` / `brick_offline_queue_v45.sqlite`) — per Brick Turso docs.
- Bulk RRA: prefer data-connector when “Register via server (RRA first)” toggle is on
- Reports pagination: repo root `QUICK_REFERENCE.md` (parent workspace)
- Riverpod perf: `.cursor/rules/flipper-riverpod-perf.mdc` + `docs/riverpod_perf.md` — `select()`, batched Ditto observers, page-scoped reports; preserve optimistic cart tap
